snippet.textDisplay: When I’m on my period I always carry extra pads, a packet of tissues in case somewhere doesn’t have toilet tissues and nappy bags. So I can dispose the pad discreetly, inside the wrapper of the new pad, tissue around it and then nappy bag knotted. If somewhere has no bin as well then it’s not icky to carry in your bag/pocket too. Hope this helps anyone.
